Your best friend, Kira, to invite you to visit her in Baumholder, a small provincial town. When planning a visit, you do not even suspect that you expect there. It all started with a generous snowfall in the middle of summer, and then there was an unusual ice castle, and to top it all around the city started to go ice golems 
and freeze everything.
